706925f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sullivan Place - Ludlam Place
706925f-a.text:
Sullivan 'Place, north side, between Ludlam Place and Rogers Av.
Now a 4-story apartment house (348-356 Rogers Ave., and 205 Sullivan Street),
occupy the Chadwick Estate. In 1890 the house faced old Bedford Road.
1870.
